Description_lang: Throw this fish back into the water and gain a stack of Bloody Chum attracting Sanguine Dogfish to your location for $d.This effect increases your odds by $s1% and stacks up to 10 times. Movement will cause your scent to be lost and cancel the effect.
AuraDescription_lang: Increasing your chance to find Sanguine Dogfish by $w2%. Movement will cause your scent to be lost and cancel this effect.
